#pragma once

#define BASIC_TOWER_DESCRIPTION "Basic tower is cheap but weak.\nBecause of its low price, it's a good choise\nto build it in the begining and upgrade it later on.\nBasic tower throws rocks at enemies which makes\nthem effective against single enemy unit however\nuseless against group of aliens."
#define SLOWING_TOWER_DESCRIPTION "Slowing tower was constructed to slow down the enemy.\nIt throws sticky mass on the ground effectivly\nslowing down the aliens. It does not deal the damage."
#define AREA_TOWER_DESCRIPTION "Area tower was invented to replace multiple basic towers.\nHowever, its power is lower than basic tower. However, it\nis irreplaceable weapon against multiple enemy units."